{"title_page": "Interior Designers Association of Nigeria", "text_new": "{{short description|Interior Designers in Nigeria}}\n\n{{Infobox organization\n| name                = International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers\n| headquarters        = [[Lagos]], [[Nigeria]]\n| board_of_directors  = Ekua Abudu, [[Titi Ogufere]], Ifeyinwa Ighodalo, Debola Omooba\n| abbreviation        = IFI\n| formation           = {{start date and age|2007}}\n| website = {{URL|https://idanng.org//}}\n}}\n\nThe '''Interior Designers Association of Nigeria''' (IDAN), is a professional body that represents professional [[Interior design|Interior Designers]] and [[Interior architecture|Interior Architects]] in [[Nigeria]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://guardian.ng/news/lagos-partners-idan-to-host-ifi-congress-november-9/|title=Lagos partners IDAN to host IFI Congress November 9|date=2017-10-28|website=The Guardian Nigeria News - Nigeria and World News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> Founded in 2007, IDAN is said to be the leading authority representing members who are mainly qualified interior designers, dealers of interior design products, finishing companies, and interior decorators. It has its headquarters in Lagos, with regional offices in [[Abuja]] and [[Port Harcourt]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://guardian.ng/guardian-woman/titi-ogufere-design-is-in-my-dna/|website=guardian.ng|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\nInterior Designers Association of Nigeria, in 2017, hosted the first ever edition of Culture and Design Festival in Africa, teaming up with 2017 congress of  [[International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers|International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers (IFI)]], a body of professional [[Interior architecture|interior architects]] and [[Interior design|interior designers]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vanguardngr.com/2017/04/trinity-verses-okowa/|title=IFI hosts World Interior Design Congress in Nigeria|date=2017-04-03|website=Vanguard News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n<references />\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|https://idanng.org/}}\n\n{{Nigeria-org-stub}}\n{{Design-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Professional associations based in Nigeria]]\n[[Category:Design institutions]]\n[[Category:Arts organizations]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Interior Designers in Nigeria}}\n\n{{Infobox organization\n| name                = International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers\n| headquarters        = [[Lagos]], [[Nigeria]]\n| board_of_directors  = Ekua Abudu, [[Titi Ogufere]], Ifeyinwa Ighodalo, Debola Omooba\n| abbreviation        = IFI\n| formation           = {{start date and age|2007}}\n| website = {{URL|https://idanng.org//}}\n}}\n\nThe '''Interior Designers Association of Nigeria''' (IDAN), is a professional body that represents professional [[Interior design|Interior Designers]] and [[Interior architecture|Interior Architects]] in [[Nigeria]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://guardian.ng/news/lagos-partners-idan-to-host-ifi-congress-november-9/|title=Lagos partners IDAN to host IFI Congress November 9|date=2017-10-28|website=The Guardian Nigeria News - Nigeria and World News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> Founded in 2007, IDAN is said to be the leading authority representing members who are mainly qualified interior designers, dealers of interior design products, finishing companies, and interior decorators. It has its headquarters in Lagos, with regional offices in [[Abuja]] and [[Port Harcourt]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://guardian.ng/guardian-woman/titi-ogufere-design-is-in-my-dna/|website=guardian.ng|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\nInterior Designers Association of Nigeria, in 2017, hosted the first ever edition of Culture and Design Festival in Africa, teaming up with 2017 congress of  [[International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers|International Federation of Interior Architects/Designers (IFI)]], a body of professional [[Interior architecture|interior architects]] and [[Interior design|interior designers]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vanguardngr.com/2017/04/trinity-verses-okowa/|title=IFI hosts World Interior Design Congress in Nigeria|date=2017-04-03|website=Vanguard News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\n<references />\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|https://idanng.org/}}\n\n{{Nigeria-org-stub}}\n{{Design-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Professional associations based in Nigeria]]\n[[Category:Design institutions]]\n[[Category:Arts organizations established]]\n", "name_user": "Ememdee", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Interior_Designers_Association_of_Nigeria"}
